{"tid":1766802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國不會進行制裁","createTime":"2019-12-03T01:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T11:47:41.000Z","uid":338032,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4387287f322384912d934072bb6f870fc08f49b5","tid":1766802,"uid":338032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:01:36.000Z","msg":"大家好，我哋之前聯署去信英國國會議員，要求制裁港共官員以及一眾黑警（15萬人聯署，名單同罪狀都交埋）。等咗幾日之後，我哋終於收到外交部嘅回信。<br />\n<br />\n早前寫嘅信，已經寄出：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720775\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720775</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">英國外交部12月2日回信明確表示，現階段唔會進行任何制裁行動！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n信中第4段列明：We note your reference to sanctions. Our focus is on supporting a peaceful resolution through meaningful dialogue that addresses the concerns of the Hong Kong people.<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪對英國外交大臣Dominic Raab好失望？！ 佢竟然認為齋吹水可以解決問題！佢早幾日爆出拒絕放寬BNO入境以外，今日竟然又再話<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不會</span></strong>制裁港共黑警！<br />\n<br />\n襯而家英國大選臨近，大家要努力推動民意，外交大臣Dominic Raab極可能議席不保！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋要合力踢走背信棄義、冇骨氣、冇承擔嘅娓共政客！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n請一齊去外交大臣Dominic Raab以及外交部FCO 嘅Twitter、Facebook 好好表達大家嘅意見！<br />\n<br />\n外交大臣Twitter:  <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DominicRaab?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDominicRaab%3Fs%3D09&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=52198820\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DominicRaab?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n外交部Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FCOHumanRights?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFCOHumanRights%3Fs%3D09&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c9b5106c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FCOHumanRights?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n入去幫拖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1201403019910356993?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1201403019910356993%3Fs%3D19&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=e81250ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1201403019910356993%3Fs%3D19&h=db911eeb\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1201403019910356993?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pL9qxJx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpL9qxJx.jpg&h=ff5d68bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6656f6edd26f52de2935a0261684860ebe273ae9","tid":1766802,"uid":338032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:03:28.000Z","msg":"之前聯署嘅post:<br />\n<br />\n英國第一批制裁名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728109\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728109</a>"},{"pid":"246b34feefac116cc244c2812adccc4d8e5697c1","tid":1766802,"uid":20809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:06:39.000Z","msg":"一早話蝧狗垃圾<br />\n<br />\n香港人7成靠自己3成靠美帝"},{"pid":"771e6ebcf58305b3551fd69d76598cdb9de31e35","tid":1766802,"uid":144001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:09:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87c5e38910ae7a69b5c5f4b526be7a01e1e31697","tid":1766802,"uid":187647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:11:01.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"e041453016b6f596730d03e2fe23aeed55dc6161","tid":1766802,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"30004639af9e954b9ef56ea976788fedbc2a6aa0","tid":1766802,"uid":332877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f7c8638bd45a87c1baa3c71d1d6e1ec20ccfde","tid":1766802,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67a